Hello everyone! has anyone here tried to add a pagination in the `simple_list_page` statement? I was planning to limit the post inside this statement but seems like it's not possible based on the HubSpot documentation, but the pagination is possible because it says that :

• simple listing is NOT affected by post limit
• simple listing CAN be paginated
are there any workaround for this without limiting the posts in the settings? here's what my blog listing code looks like

```  {% if tag %}
   {# inside here will be the list of tag related articles #}

  {% elif not simple_list_page %}
   {# inside here will be the homepage of the blog listing #}

  {% elif simple_list_page %}
   {# inside here will be the listing of the /all articles #}
  {% endif %}```
